text: Violeta Bernotaitė (born 4 April 1965) is a Lithuanian rower. She competed in the women's coxless pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Lithuanian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Lithuania Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Viekšniai
